&lt;h2 id="什么是-acp">什么是 ACP？&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>ACP (Agent Client Protocol) 让 OpenClaw 能调用外部编码工具（Claude Code、Codex 等）。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>OpenClaw 快捷键速查表</title><link>https://bluespace.eu.org/post/%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99/openclaw%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%94%AE/</link><pubDate>Fri, 10 Apr 2026 02:16:14 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://bluespace.eu.org/post/%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99/openclaw%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E9%94%AE/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="openclaw-快捷键速查表">OpenClaw 快捷键速查表&lt;/h1>
